Located at the sensual My Khe beachfront, Yarra Ocean Suites Danang offers 102 modern rooms overlooking the spectacular waves overlapping the pristine white sand. Inspired by the vibrant Danang coastline, the sweeping oceanfront offers a great view for an extended stay and only steps away from the bustling Danang city life.
