Great location and staff
I‚Äôve stayed at Hiltons, Marriotts and Hyatts around the world, and the staff at Yarra are top notch. One employee Tan Hoang was the highlight of our stay, highlighting what hospitality really stands for. Was always able and willing to go above and beyond on making our stay more comfortable and answering any questions. The hotel is across the street from the beach, and behind it is all the foreign restaurants, so many English speaking businesses and food (Mexican, American, French and of course Vietnamese or Korean). There‚Äôs a pool on the rooftop, free breakfast with wide selection each morning that changes. Windows of room could be cleaned but I believe it's film placed over them that may need to be removed. Overall highly recommend this hotel at the high value for money paid.
